name: 2021 Goal Posters
description:
I've been thinking a lot about my resolutions for 2021 — thought it'd be fun to share a goal poster template for folks who like to visualize their goals. I made this for a friend who said he struggles with creating daily habits; I thought maybe he could print this out and post it up as a visual reminder.


Would love to see your remixes or even your own goals for 2021 ✨
